                "post_title": "Love and Relationships",
                "post_name": "love-and-relationships",
                "post_parent": "",
                "ID": 2071,
                "post_content": "<span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;People fall in love and make relationships. They do it because they wish to live happier than before. They expect to compliment and complete each other. Even though every man and woman wishes so, sometimes they break up.\\n Even though they wish to be together forever, they part.\\n The author of the book also has gone through similar situations and has seen many such ones. Upon observing them, he sees that every story is worth doing research on.\\n That is the objective behind this writing venture. The author tries to capture the moments when people fall in love and when they break apart. He tries to find the reasons behind. He tries to research on relationships.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:7165,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:[null,2,13421772]},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;6&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:[null,2,13421772]},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;7&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:[null,2,13421772]},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;8&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:[null,2,13421772]},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;9&quot;:0,&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;14&quot;:[null,2,0],&quot;15&quot;:&quot;\\&quot;Times New Roman\\&quot;, serif&quot;}\">People fall in love and make relationships. They do it because they wish to live happier than before. They expect to compliment and complete each other. Even though every man and woman wishes so, sometimes they break up.\nEven though they wish to be together forever, they part.\nThe author of the book also has gone through similar situations and has seen many such ones. Upon observing them, he sees that every story is worth doing research on.\nThat is the objective behind this writing venture. The author tries to capture the moments when people fall in love and when they break apart. He tries to find the reasons behind. He tries to research on relationships.</span>",
