                "ID": 2116,
                "post_content": "<span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;15th August 1947, the date is ingrained in every Indian's mind.\\n Jana gana mana....... The sound floated in the air. Swaraj was rejoiced with singing of the anthem.\\n Swaraj in all its coming years saw ups and downs, many events shaped our free India.\\n The ills of Partition, Corruption, Dowry, Girl infanticide, Emergency, Reservation and Riots booed us down.\\n The bright side to it were Middle class emergence, Women empowerment, Liberalisation, India's surge towards economic progress.\\n All these factors were entwined with Swaraj the central character, in a happy coincidence.\\n The growth of independent India is filtered through the lens of Swaraj, the common Indian.\\n With Jana gana mana...... It all began\\n With Jana gana mana...... It all ends.\\n Paying its tribute to the rising nation.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:14730,&quot;4&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:16777215},&quot;6&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:[null,2,0]},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;14&quot;:[null,2,0],&quot;15&quot;:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;16&quot;:10}\">15th August 1947, the date is ingrained in every Indian's mind.\nJana gana mana....... The sound floated in the air. Swaraj was rejoiced with singing of the anthem.\nSwaraj in all its coming years saw ups and downs, many events shaped our free India.\nThe ills of Partition, Corruption, Dowry, Girl infanticide, Emergency, Reservation, and Riots booed us down.\nThe bright side to it was Middle-class emergence, Women empowerment, Liberalisation, India's surge towards economic progress.\nAll these factors were entwined with Swaraj the central character, in a happy coincidence.\nThe growth of independent India is filtered through the lens of Swaraj, the common Indian.\nWith Jana gana mana...... It all began\nWith Jana gana mana...... It all ends.\nPaying its tribute to the rising nation.</span>",
