                "ID": 2138,
                "post_content": "&nbsp;\n\n<style type=\"text/css\"><!--td {border: 1px solid #ccc;}br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--></style>\n\n<span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;A tale of love and motivation. This is a tale of a mother and her speech impaired daughter. Reshmi is a seventeen-year old girl. God has endowed her with angelic beauty but took her ability to speak. Nature is her only friend. Every day sitting by the river she talks to her through her poetry. One day, Nature plays a trick on her. The mute girl falls in love. Her mother is aghast because she now believes her innocent daughter has to suffer. Meanwhile, they discover an incurable, fatal disease is hurling Reshmi towards a tremendously painful death. Reshmi is not afraid but her eyes keep sparkling with thousands of dreams. Lying on her death bed, she finds herself living beyond this world.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:7165,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:13421772}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;6&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:13421772}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;7&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:13421772}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;8&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:[{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;5&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:13421772}},{&quot;1&quot;:0,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;3&quot;:3},{&quot;1&quot;:1,&quot;2&quot;:0,&quot;4&quot;:1}]},&quot;9&quot;:0,&quot;10&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;14&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0},&quot;15&quot;:&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;}\">A tale of love and motivation. This is a tale of a mother and her speech impaired daughter. Reshmi is a seventeen-year old girl. God has endowed her with angelic beauty but took her ability to speak. Nature is her only friend. Every day sitting by the river she talks to her through her poetry. One day, Nature plays a trick on her. The mute girl falls in love. Her mother is aghast because she now believes her innocent daughter has to suffer. Meanwhile, they discover an incurable, fatal disease is hurling Reshmi towards a tremendously painful death. Reshmi is not afraid but her eyes keep sparkling with thousands of dreams. Lying on her death bed, she finds herself living beyond this world.</span>",
