                "ID": 2139,
                "post_content": "Does life ever give us a second chance? A chance to change things, to make them different somehow? Or does it only give us a chance, just to accept things the way they are, and make peace with it? Does it seem fair, when we start feeling robbed of all the things that once gave us a reason to feel alive?These are just some of the questions Arjun has to face, after a dire tragedy threatens to choke the life out of his existence. Does he manage to find any answers? Does he succeed in finding out the true meaning of choice, and destiny? Or does he succumb to the menacing void left in his life? A void, that threatens to wipe out everything and everyone around him.The Orange Sky is a story about love, longing and the unforeseen complexities of life. A story about how we try to find our way home, one way or the other.",
