                "post_content": "Pocket Of Smile\"\" is a collection of soul-enchanting verses with several conversations to toss out the wrenched thoughts and reach the pinnacle of self-realization and peace.\n\nIt is the journey of a woman recollecting her memories while she is inside the pocket of smile and each day she makes a promise to be happy and smile irrespective of any obstacles she is going through. Sometimes we feel ourselves so much cocooned and suffocated that we donÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t allow our emotions to live the way they want, and this is where few pages from Pocket of Smile are taken out to help them to emote the way they want to get re-kindled.\nIt is an emotional walk that depicts the many facets of life and the emotional ups and downs that the soul experiences before emerging and breathing freely after being sidetracked so frequently. She walked from an abstract place to this earthly world to realize herself and get the courage to stand independently. Poems use metaphors of many shades of life to weave many threads for the soul, like joy, happiness, love, grief, pain, loneliness, success, rejection, acceptance, expectations, expressions, life, hatred, and moments when she finally meets her soul.",
